1. Normalize the Rule Text (Most Important Step)

Different users write the same rule differently:

Produce error if CustomerName is null and length > 20
CustomerName must not be null and length greater than 20
Raise error when CustomerName missing and length exceeds 20

Normalize them using rule standardization.

Steps
	1.	Convert to lowercase
	2.	Remove filler words
	3.	Standardize operators
	4.	Standardize rule keywords

Example transformation:
Produce error if CustomerName is null and length > 20
Normalize:
customername null length > 20
